距离实验¶

  1. 欧式距离
  2. 城区距离
  3. 棋盘距离

欧式距离实验¶

公式¶

$distance = \sqrt{(x-s)^2 + (y-t)^2 }$

In [ ]:
from skimage import data, io 
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import math



img = data.coffee()

cy = int(img.shape[0]/2)
cx = int(img.shape[1]/2)
print(cy, cx)

distance = 100

for i in range(img.shape[0]):
    for j in range(img.shape[1]):
        for k in range(img.shape[2]):
            if math.sqrt(  (cy-i)**2  + (cx-j)**2   ) <=  distance:
                img[i,j,k] = 0
# plt.figure(dpi=200)
plt.imshow(img)
plt.show()

城区距离实验¶

公式¶

$distance = |x-s| + |y-t|$

In [ ]:
from skimage import data, io 
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import math



img = data.astronaut()

cy = int(img.shape[0]/2)
cx = int(img.shape[1]/2)
print(cy, cx)

distance = 100

for i in range(img.shape[0]):
    for j in range(img.shape[1]):
        for k in range(img.shape[2]):
            if (abs(cy-i)  + abs(cx-j)) <=  distance:
                img[i,j,k] = 0
# plt.figure(dpi=200)
plt.imshow(img)
plt.show()

棋盘距离实验¶

公式¶

$distance = max(|x-s|, |y-t|)$

In [ ]:
from skimage import data, io 
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import math



img = data.chelsea()

cy = int(img.shape[0]/2)
cx = int(img.shape[1]/2)
print(cy, cx)

distance = 50

for i in range(img.shape[0]):
    for j in range(img.shape[1]):
        for k in range(img.shape[2]):
            if max(abs(cy-i), abs(cx-j)) <=  distance:
                img[i,j,k] = 0
# plt.figure(dpi=200)
plt.imshow(img)
plt.show()
